author: hdu
msg: fix the annotations of to-be-ignored automatic tests
The JUNIT @Ignore annotations are further processed in XMLReporter.xsl
using the regular expression "(.*)#(\d+)(.*)" to find an eventual issue
reference or other details, so an annotation should^ follow this pattern.
